{"tid":1193160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6.9遊行 迫人表態真係咁重要？....","createTime":"2019-06-08T18:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T01:59:32.000Z","uid":207000,"like":36,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"45c140a8b9cd5b041d3fd1ca800ac172510a1f76","tid":1193160,"uid":207000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:49:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港有言論自由<br />\n我地都捍衛緊呢份自由</span></span><br />\n而我唔明白嘅係<br />\n點解要迫人表態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係咁重要咩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迫個啞嘅表態真係咁重要咩<br />\n我覺得唔重要<br />\n完全係哂時間...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n今日見到大家係到屌黎屌去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過留返啲精力 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臨訓睇多幾次個啲教人聽日點保護好自己嘅post仲好</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">身為香港人 發出自己嘅聲音係好重要<br />\n但<span style=\"color: gold;\">保護好自己都好重要</span></span><br />\n另外 企係同一個立場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">見到youtuber 海外嘅港人 upload 片撐反送中<br />\n係一件<span style=\"color: red;\">振奮 提升凝聚力</span>嘅事</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇出聲個啲咪由佢囉<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">得返咁少時間 出聲嘅讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為多一份影響力係到<br />\n冇出聲嘅 唔洗下下屌<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">留返精力聽日一齊加油<br />\n留返精力去鼓勵更多同一立場嘅人出黎仲好啦..</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我係連登做開花生友 但距離遊行剩返唔夠一日<br />\n都仲見到好多無謂嘅嘈交</span><br />\n真係睇見都攰 所以第一次咁樣開po留低自己嘅想法<br />\n好撚多固執撚 好撚多膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由佢地啦屌 講多無謂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我都係固執撚 不過我覺得我企啱立場</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日見 加油 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同埋見到香港人係咁短時間<br />\n做咗咁多傳單 咁多宣傳</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（宣傳仲要同班收錢嘅嘈）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好自豪 你地話我岸久都好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我都係好自豪咁講<br />\n我愛香港人 呢個地方幾辛苦都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有你地真係好開心 </span><br />\n<br />\n預咗比人搵位屌 我只不過想分享我嘅意見<br />\n屌得舒服嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">隨便 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">同同一立場嘅香港人講聲 聽日見</span><br />\n黎唔到嘅 都希望為遊行嘅人加油<br />\n多一個唔多 少一個唔少？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實邊理得咁多😂😂<br />\n我都只係做我認為啱嘅事 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係一個土生土長嘅香港人🔥<br />\n點講都好 都唔想移民嘅香港人<br />\n同你地立場衝突都好 <br />\n想屌就屌 <span style=\"color: red;\">你有你道理 <br />\n我有我理由。</span>"},{"pid":"a8c9eb2bd35641a6276e1242b36faf9e07849926","tid":1193160,"uid":236140,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T18:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ky2aN6Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKy2aN6Y.png&h=e5ba8173&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjwbxyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhjwbxyD.png&h=ef28aad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明天見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9afc5ac626aa9e593aad8629203e5fe711b020f